CatDescriptText: image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, January 9, 1960, pg. A9, reads: "Other Models who made the interracial fashion show at the D.I.'s party a beautiful event were Karen Seibert and Roseann Dimperico. Here, they head for home with the models' badge...the hat box, and bright smiles."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of Karen Seibert and Roseann Dimperico, carrying hat boxes, standing in interior of the New Arena Supper Club for the D.I.'s National Foundation benefit
